OL,7,FHe added: "You can't allow yourself to
OL,8,Fpanic or get flustered because it's a
OL,9,Fvery critical amount you have to get
OL,10,Fthe tourniquet on so you won't bleed
OL,11,Fto death."
OL,13,FTom started starting volunteering in
OL,14,FUkraine 2023 when he drove a vehicle
OL,15,Ffull of donations and medical supplies
OL,16,Ffrom Hull.
OL,18,FHe returned again in 2024 and started
OL,19,Fdriving displaced families to
OL,20,Fdifferent parts of the country.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
