OL,5,Cfrontline
OL,7,FIn March this year, he decided to join
OL,8,Fthe The National Guard of Ukraine as a
OL,9,Fvolunteer and was placed in the Donbas
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,F"I wanted to do something to help the
OL,13,Fpeople of Ukraine, I didn't like the
OL,14,Fidea of Russia being able to bully its
OL,15,Fneighbour and bomb schools and
OL,16,Fhospitals," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
