OL,4,CUkraine 'determined' to go back to
OL,5,Cfrontline
OL,7,FTom said he opted for amputation as he
OL,8,Fwould be more likely to be able to
OL,9,Fwalk and run unsupported with a
OL,10,Fprosthetic.
OL,12,F"In my head I had already decided it
OL,13,Fwas gone, so it wasn't too difficult
OL,14,Fto go through with the procedure. But
OL,15,Fit was definitely weird to wake up
OL,16,Fwithout one of your limbs, even if
OL,17,Fyou've already thought about it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
