OL,3,CBritish volunteer who lost foot in
OL,4,CUkraine 'determined' to go back to
OL,5,Cfrontline
OL,7,FHe said: "A lot of people have asked
OL,8,Fwhy I don't come back to the UK? Why I
OL,9,Fhaven't already come back to the UK?
OL,11,F"I don't want to just give up after
OL,12,Fthe first injury and allow the enemy
OL,13,Fto have injured me, and then I go home
OL,14,Fand call it a day.
OL,16,F"There's still a lot of work to be
OL,17,Fdone here. There's still a lot of
OL,18,Ffighting going on. Ukraine needs a lot
OL,19,Fof help. And, there's still a lot of
OL,20,Fwork to be done. There's still a war
OL,21,Fgoing on that hasn't changed."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
